</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FA2736D177325B6FDDCD13A3FEA09330" blockId="5.[188,1399,448,581]" pageId="5" pageNumber="77">
<taxonomicName id="3D984D5277325B6FDDCD13A3FCE690AF" authority="O.L.M.Silva &amp; Riina" authorityName="O. L. M. Silva &amp; Riina" box="[189,812,448,474]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="5" pageNumber="77" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longipenduculata" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="C8ECEAC377325B6FDDCD13A3FDDC90AF" box="[189,534,448,474]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="77">Euphorbia longipenduculata</emphasis>
O.L.M.Silva &amp; Riina
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="D3DF57B877325B6FDE4A13A2FC5690AE" box="[826,924,449,475]" pageId="5" pageNumber="77" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is most closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="3D984D5277325B6FD98913A3FE7F9088" authority="Boiss." authorityName="Boiss." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="5" pageNumber="77" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="potentilloides">
<emphasis id="C8ECEAC377325B6FD98913A3FE979088" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="77">Euphorbia potentilloides</emphasis>
Boiss.
</taxonomicName>
, but differs in its orbicular leaves, long-pedunculate cyathia (
<quantity id="3D609B3477325B6FD9C71380FAE4908B" box="[1207,1326,483,510]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="77" unit="mm" value="7.5" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="5.0">5–10 mm</quantity>
long, reaching up to 
<quantity id="3D609B3477325B6FDC191064FE719357" box="[361,443,519,546]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" pageId="5" pageNumber="77" unit="mm" value="45.0">45 mm</quantity>
long when the cyathium is fully developed) and longer cyathial gland appendages (ca 3 × 
<quantity id="3D609B3477325B6FDC651048FE949330" box="[277,350,555,581]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="77" unit="mm" value="4.0">4 mm</quantity>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
